<doc>
  <member name="VMR_ASPECT_RATIO_MODE">
    <summary>
      <para>The <b>VMR_ASPECT_RATIO_MODE</b> enumeration type describes whether the <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/DirectShow/video-mixing-renderer-filter-7">Video Mixing Renderer Filter 7</a> preserves the aspect ratio of the source video.</para>
    </summary>
    <seealso href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/DirectShow/directshow-enumerated-types">DirectShow Enumerated Types</seealso>
    <seealso cref="IVMRAspectRatioControl Interface" />
    <seealso cref="IVMRWindowlessControl Interface" />
  </member>
  <member name="VMR_ASPECT_RATIO_MODE.VMR_ARMODE_NONE">
    <summary>
      <para>Indicates that the VMR will not try to maintain the aspect ratio of the source video.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="VMR_ASPECT_RATIO_MODE.VMR_ARMODE_LETTER_BOX">
    <summary>
      <para>Indicates that the VMR will maintain the aspect ratio of the source video by letterboxing within the output rectangle.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
</doc>